solution.p:
\int\frac{\sqrt{x^2-2}}{x^2}\dee{x}&=\int\frac{\sqrt{2\sec^2\theta-2}}{2\sec^2\theta}\sqrt{2}\sec\theta\tan\theta \dee{\theta}

&=\int
