&=\frac{1}{3}\log|x+1| - \frac{1}{6}\log|x^2-x+1| +
\frac{2}{3}\int\frac{1}{\left(\frac{2x-1}{\sqrt{3}}\right)^2+1} \dee{x}

Let u= \frac{2x-1}{\sqrt3}, \dee{u} = \frac{2}{\sqrt 3}\dee{x}.

