&=3x^3 \arcsin x - 3\int\frac{x^2}{\sqrt{1-x^2}}\cdot x\dee{x}
&=3x^3 \arcsin x + \frac{3}{2}\int\frac{1-u}{\sqrt{u}}\dee{u}
